data.description: Charming & Cozy 3 bedroom and 2 bathroom with 2 car garage. Home features living room, dinning room, stainless steel appliances, laminate flooring throughout, breakfast bar and hurricane shutters. The backyard has plenty room for a pool and to entertain friends and family. Easy access to shopping, schools, restaurants, Charlotte Harbor & Downtown Punta Gorda. Call for your private showing today...
